   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Inclusive School System</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">HHCS in collaboration with ARPD has started an elementary school in April 2019 for the children with physical disabilities and children without disabilities. The idea behind the school is to provide quality education to children with disabilities in an inclusive setting, where they learn in a safe and friendly environment, and excel in life with confidence. The school has eight rooms,  computer lab and a playground. The entire school building and playground are wheelchair accessible.</narrative>
